WEBVTT

00:00.091 --> 00:02.388
Previously on "Dead of Summer"...

00:02.438 --> 00:04.111
I love this camp.
All my first were here.

00:04.161 --> 00:07.160
First girlfriend,
first kiss. First everything.

00:07.210 --> 00:09.348
If it was so great, why only one summer?

00:09.398 --> 00:11.573
My dad was killed in the
line of duty in '82.

00:11.705 --> 00:12.795
I'm sorry.

00:12.845 --> 00:14.295
Down by the lake, I saw these people.

00:14.345 --> 00:15.611
They were wearing these masks.

00:15.661 --> 00:17.615
Jack Sykes. This belonged to my father.

00:17.665 --> 00:18.858
He was doing the same thing we are.

00:18.957 --> 00:21.766
Carolina Maria Diaz,
if you wish to communicate

00:21.816 --> 00:23.592
with us, please give us a sign.

00:25.334 --> 00:26.501
You should have killed Amy

00:26.551 --> 00:28.035
when you had the chance.

00:28.085 --> 00:29.829
Did you not just see
what happened to Amy?

00:29.879 --> 00:30.950
She was possessed.

00:31.000 --> 00:32.253
What happened to me?

00:32.304 --> 00:33.338
We woke something up.

00:33.707 --> 00:34.783
Something bad.

